base times height.

00:02:38.210 --> 00:02:40.560
That's what the area of a
parallelogram would be.

00:02:40.560 --> 00:02:44.040
Now what are the base and the
height in this situation?

00:02:44.040 --> 00:02:45.640
Let me write this down.

00:02:45.640 --> 00:02:48.850
The area of our parallelogram
