00:05:49.870 --> 00:05:51.530
We're just doing the Pythagorean
theorem.

00:05:51.530 --> 00:05:52.870
This squared plus this
squared is going

00:05:52.870 --> 00:05:54.320
to equal that squared.

00:05:54.320 --> 00:06:01.930
It's going to be equal to the
length of v2 squared.

00:06:01.930 --> 00:06:03.410
That's just the Pythagorean
theorem.

00:06:07.670 --> 00:06:10.550
Nothing fancy there.

00:06:10.550 --> 00:06:11.740
So how can we simplify?

00:06:11.740 --> 00:06:14.470
We want to solve for H.

